org.gradoop.common.model.impl.properties.strategies

Class PropertyValueStrategyFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.common.model.impl.properties.strategies.PropertyValueStrategyFactory

  • public class PropertyValueStrategyFactory
extends Object
    Factory class responsible for instantiating strategy classes that manage every kind of access to the current PropertyValue value.

      • fromRawBytes

        public static Object fromRawBytes(byte[] bytes)
        Returns value which is represented by the the provided byte array. Assumes that the value is serialized according to the PropertyValue standard.
        Parameters:

        Returns:
        Object which is the result of the deserialization.

      • compare

        public static int compare(Object value,
                          Object other)
        Compares two values. If other is not comparable to value, the used PropertyValueStrategy will throw an IllegalArgumentException.
        Parameters:
        value - first value.
        other - second value.
        Returns:
        a negative integer, zero, or a positive integer as value is less than, equal to, or greater than other.

      • getRawBytes

        public static byte[] getRawBytes(Object value)
        Get byte array representation of the provided object. The object is serialized according to the PropertyValue standard. If the given type is not supported, an UnsupportedTypeException will be thrown.
        Parameters:
        value - to be serialized.
        Returns:
        byte array representation of the provided object.

      • get

        public static PropertyValueStrategy get(byte value)
                                 throws UnsupportedTypeException
        Returns strategy mapping to the provided byte value.
        Parameters:
        value - representing a data type.
        Returns:
        strategy class.
        Throws:
        UnsupportedTypeException - when there is no matching strategy for a given type byte.

      • get

        public static PropertyValueStrategy get(Class clazz)
                                 throws UnsupportedTypeException
        Get a strategy which corresponds the provided class. If there is no mapping for the provided class in the class-strategy map, or the value of the parameter is null, an instance of NullStrategy is returned.
        Parameters:
        clazz - some class
        Returns:
        strategy class which is able to handle the provided type.
        Throws:
        UnsupportedTypeException - when there is no matching strategy for the given class.

      • get

        public static PropertyValueStrategy get(Object value)
                                 throws UnsupportedTypeException
        Get strategy by object.
        Parameters:
        value - some object.
        Returns:
        strategy that handles operations on the provided object type. If value is null, NullStrategy is returned.
        Throws:
        UnsupportedTypeException - when there is no matching strategy for a given object.
